body_html: This is not really possible since decode ops are usually expected to be done in host language, and it would be likely be more efficient to do it before invoking tensorflow in any case. This is because there is usually much faster since there are platform specific accelerations (even so as much as to make the camera output smaller images in the first place). So closing as expected behavior.
